------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party data sources
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product uses data derived from public sources. It is not endorsed or
certified by any of them.

- The Movie Database (TMDB). This product uses the TMDB API and TMDB data
  but is not endorsed or certified by TMDB. https://www.themoviedb.org/
- Box Office Mojo / The Numbers — worldwide box-office figures used for
  comparable-title economics.
- Motion Picture Association (MPA) THEME Report — global theatrical market
  sizing.

Generated film/series concepts cite primary sources inline; the engine's
veracity layer verifies each external number against the cited page.

